Subject: [PATCH] Fix portability issues on *BSD and MacOS

(cherry picked from commit 2478dbdfba7cf729ddee43a5a77bde8c25ccdede)
(cherry picked from commit 84bbb4d8164aae21a8e5418250359637d8aabc29)
